ay and bring it inside at night. Also great for rural areas where you might move it to follow the sun.\n            </p>\n            <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07JPH4PHG?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block mt-3 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-flame text-white text-sm font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-flame/90 transition-colors\">\n              Check Price →\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      \n      <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-5 rounded-xl shadow-lg\">\n        <div class=\"w-full h-36 mb-3\">\n          <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71QAZC6XFwL._AC_UY218_.jpg\" alt=\"ALLPOWERS 100W Foldable Panel\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-full object-contain bg-slate-50\" />\n        </div>\n        <h3 data-asin=\"B08DKTZY7G\" class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-1\">ALLPOWERS 100W Foldable</h3>\n        <span class=\"bg-lime text-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold\">4.2★</span>\n        <span class=\"ml-1 text-slate-500 text-xs\">$$$$</span>\n        <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs mt-2\">\n          23% efficiency, IP66 waterproof. Compact design pairs well with power stations. Great for charging batteries and devices.\n        </p>\n        <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08DKTZY7G?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block mt-2 text-flame text-sm font-medium no-underline hover:underline\">\n          View →\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    \n    <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg mt-5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4\">\n      <div class=\"w-full sm:w-36 shrink-0\">\n        <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/91V1NeY3VxL._AC_UY218_.jpg\" alt=\"YT30 30W Foldable Solar Charger\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-36 object-contain bg-slate-50\" />\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\n        <h3 data-asin=\"B0FL7FCG5D\" class=\"text-base font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-1\">YT30 30W Foldable Charger</h3>\n        <span class=\"bg-lime text-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold\">4.3★</span>\n        <span class=\"ml-1 text-slate-500 text-xs\">$$$</span>\n        <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mt-2\">\n          The \"just charge my phone\" option. QC3.0 USB plus DC output with 10 different connectors. IP65 waterproof. At $$$ it's an affordable add-on to any larger system, or a standalone solution for basic device charging. Fits in a backpack.\n        </p>\n        <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FL7FCG5D?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block mt-2 text-flame text-sm font-medium no-underline hover:underline\">\n          View →\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-slate-800 text-white p-5 md:p-8 rounded-2xl mb-10\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4\">The Whole-House Solution</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-slate-300 mb-6\">For families who want to essentially go off-grid, there's this beast:</p>\n    \n    <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 bg-white/10 p-5 rounded-xl\">\n      <div class=\"w-full md:w-56 shrink-0\">\n        <img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81audnUHPBL._AC_UY218_.jpg\" alt=\"ECO-WORTHY 9.36KWH Complete Solar System\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"rounded-lg w-full h-56 object-contain bg-white/20\" />\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\n        <span class=\"bg-flame text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase mb-3 inline-block\">Maximum Power</span>\n        <h3 data-asin=\"B0BQV4YG1T\" class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2\">ECO-WORTHY 9.36KWH Complete System</h3>\n        <span class=\"bg-lime text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold\">4.4★ (445 reviews)</span>\n        <span class=\"ml-2 text-slate-300 text-sm\">$$$$$</span>\n        <p class=\"text-slate-200 mt-4 mb-3\">\n          <span class=\"text-5xl font-extrabold text-sunglow\">2,340W</span> of solar panels. 9.36 kilowatt-hours of storage. 5,000W inverter. This is a full home backup system.\n        </p>\n        <p class=\"text-slate-300 text-sm mb-4\">\n          Twelve 195W panels, 48V all-in-one charge inverter, mounting brackets—plug and play at massive scale. This could run a refrigerator, multiple fans, lights, TV, and still have capacity left over. The shipping cost will be significant, and installation requires real electrical knowledge. But if you're serious about energy independence for your family, this is the endgame.\n        </p>\n        <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BQV4YG1T?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-sunglow text-raisin font-bold no-underline hover:bg-sunglow/90 transition-colors\">\n          See Full System →\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"my-10\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4\">Compare Your Top Choices</h2>\n    <product-comparison products=\"B0FG2VF2V2,B0BPY72B9R,B0FFGTMG46,B0FZKR417P\">\n  </product-comparison></section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"my-10\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4\">Estimate Shipping Costs</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4\">Solar panels are heavy. Factor this into your budget before buying.</p>\n    <shipping-calculator products=\"B0FG2VF2V2,B0BPY72B9R,B0FFGTMG46,B07JPH4PHG,B08DKTZY7G\" destination=\"all\">\n  </shipping-calculator></section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"bg-raisin text-white p-5 md:p-8 rounded-2xl mt-10 not-prose\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4\">The Bottom Line</h2>\n    <p class=\"text-slate-200 text-lg mb-4\">\n      For most families, the <span class=\"text-sunglow font-bold\">Renogy 400W Premium Kit</span> hits the sweet spot: enough power for essentials, MPPT efficiency, Bluetooth monitoring you can help with remotely, and that perfect 5-star rating across 500+ reviews. If budget is tighter but you need more watts, the <span class=\"text-lime font-semibold\">18BB 800W panels at $$$</span> are genuinely impressive value—just add your own controller.\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"text-slate-300 mb-6\">\n      Skip the plug-and-play grid-tie systems unless the grid is reliable (it's not). And whatever you choose, confirm someone in the family can handle the installation before you ship it.\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-3\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FG2VF2V2?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-sunglow text-raisin font-bold no-underline hover:bg-sunglow/90 transition-colors\">\n        Get the Renogy 400W →\n      </a>\n      <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FFGTMG46?tag=veguitas-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-white/20 text-white font-semibold no-underline hover:bg-white/30 transition-colors\">\n        See the 800W Budget Pick →\n      </a>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"mt-10\">\n    <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4\">Your Solar Shopping Checklist</h2>\n    <checklist-builder>\n  </checklist-builder></section>\n\n</article>"
